resources UK(12)
notes
The experiment is for SuperDARN technique development of the thermospheric 
neutral density measurement by the CUTLASS radar. In parallel, optical 
observations will occur during the second half of each experiment. Heater 
operations will stop when the ionosphere goes under-dense.
